Answer the telephone.

01:04:29.680 --> 01:04:32.960
Hello? Who?

01:04:33.000 --> 01:04:35.000
Mr. Maloney?

01:04:35.080 --> 01:04:38.080
Barlow Creek?
Go ahead.

01:04:38.160 --> 01:04:41.080
Hello.

